{"tid":2001023,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊永強：本港過去兩周沒本地個案　繼續戴口罩作用不大","createTime":"2020-05-04T08:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T14:35:41.000Z","uid":166360,"like":59,"dislike":203,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"a8b386aefb91236c54948d639d164a1ede083de8","tid":2001023,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T08:47:17.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】中大公共衞生及基層醫療學院講座教授楊永強認為，本港過去兩周沒有本地個案，繼續戴口罩作用不大。<br />\n<br />\n在零三年沙士期間擔任衞生福利及食物局局長的楊永強表示，本港現時情況與沙士相當不同，當時香港對新疫情完全沒有準備，隔離病房和保護衣物不足；政府於沙士後檢討如何避免日後大爆發，增加了隔離病房，醫護保護裝備預留三個月存貨以及成立衞生防護中心做預防工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=389817\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D389817&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1r2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=277db2aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D389817&h=f1189b49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=389817</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">信專家，唔戴! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6e64e2bbc9b8900cec93bb733902a2ad18ff8b1f","tid":2001023,"uid":28181,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T08:48:35.000Z","msg":"信陳雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老師又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d027f143bfe2d82c19b4c1816d72624c565812","tid":2001023,"uid":7789,"like":125,"dislike":1,"score":124,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T08:49:26.000Z","msg":"經過沙士仲有邊個信呢條壽頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe9b9e24e4232af1fca0a284cca187274412c3c","tid":2001023,"uid":2054,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"17d027f143bfe2d82c19b4c1816d72624c565812","tid":2001023,"uid":7789,"like":125,"dislike":1,"scor